text: Authors' contributions RY, SC, ST and YY carried out the animal studies, performed the data and statistical analysis. ST, SC and RY drafted the manuscript. KM supervised and carried out the experiments regarding isolation of CD45-and CD45+ lung cells. MK participated in coordination of the study, acquiring funding and helped writing the manuscript. TS coordinated and designed the study and wrote the final manuscript. All authors read and approved the final manuscript.
